        }
      },
      "Effects": [
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 0.0,
          "Message": "\" The Buddhist Cats \" : A quiet faction living out through hidden veils of the Whisperfrost Frontiers."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 3.0,
          "Message": "\" The Buddhist Cats \" : These Felidarians are one of the few factions who have mastered full healing. Able to break any curse, disease, or magically disability."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 7.0,
          "Message": "\" The Buddhist Cats \" : However, only a select few of people have ever witnessed them. To average person, these people may not exis. . ."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
