        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 3.0,
          "Message": "\" One of a Kind Bladist \" : Agni holds the Alterverse record of 100 undefeated duels. Many know she only lost because she was exhausted from that many battles."
