      },
      "Effects": [
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 0.0,
          "Message": "\" Agni's Legacy \" :  Lady Agni comes from a long linage of swordsman. Even from a young age she showed swift and agile cuts with the blade."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 3.0,
          "Message": "\" Agni's Legacy \" :  Born with four older brothers, Agni always danced around in the rough house. The youngest she may be, but the most ferocious of her family."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 7.0,
          "Message": "\" Agni's Legacy \" :  Her qualities made her an dangerous opponent. It is always best to stay in line while in her presences."
        },
