          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 0.0,
          "Message": "\" The Builder is Here \" : Zerk is one of the most renown builders in Alterverse."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 3.0,
          "Message": "\" The Builder is Here \" : When in his avatar powers, many have described it as a burst of joy with lights and people smiling."
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 7.0,
          "Message": "\" The Builder is Here \" : Personally, I had the pleasure of seeing his work help my community. We come from a weaker coms. . ."
