          "Delay": 0.0,
          "Message": "\" The First Ones \" : If you weren't some of the first people at the Grand Ceremony, then you may have missed out meeting some of the greatest avatars!"
        },
        {
          "Type": "SendMessage",
          "Event": "ENTER",
          "Interval": 0.0,
          "Delay": 3.0,
          "Message": "\" The First Ones \" : Zerk arrived promptly on time being the FIRST. ---- who started the ceremony surprisngly was SECOND to her own ceremony. "
